structured.title: Discussion On Political Labeling And Extremism
structured.overview: The brief conversation features a German-speaking participant objecting to being labeled a Nazi or right-wing extremist, insisting instead that he is a concerned citizen worried about cultural over-foreignization. He criticizes how quickly the Nazi label is used when arguments run out.
